<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Custom Pricing & Loyalty App</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                        <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">CP</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Custom Pricing & Loyalty App</h1>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">For Shopify</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">
                    Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Last updated: <span class="font-medium">December 13, 2024</span></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
            
            <!-- Introduction -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    This Privacy Policy describes how Custom Pricing & Loyalty App ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and shares your personal information when you use our Shopify application.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Information We Collect -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    1. Information We Collect
                </h2>
                
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">1.1 Information from Shopify</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">When you install our app, we collect:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Store information (store name, domain, email)</li>
                    <li>Customer information (names, email addresses, customer IDs)</li>
                    <li>Product information (product titles, variants, prices)</li>
                    <li>Order information (order details, order amounts)</li>
                    <li>API access tokens to communicate with your Shopify store</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">1.2 Information You Provide</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Custom pricing rules you create</li>
                    <li>Loyalty program settings and configurations</li>
                    <li>Points and tier adjustments</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">1.3 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Log data (IP addresses, browser type, access times)</li>
                    <li>App usage data (features used, actions taken)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- How We Use Information -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    2. How We Use Your Information
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">We use the collected information to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Provide and maintain the app functionality</li>
                    <li>Apply custom pricing to products for specific customers</li>
                    <li>Manage loyalty points and reward programs</li>
                    <li>Create draft orders with custom pricing</li>
                    <li>Generate discount codes for loyalty redemptions</li>
                    <li>Send notifications about loyalty points and rewards</li>
                    <li>Improve and optimize app performance</li>
                    <li>Provide customer support</li>
                    <li>Detect and prevent fraud or abuse</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Data Sharing -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
                </h2>
                
                <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
                    <p class="text-blue-900 font-medium">
                        We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">We may share your information only in the following cases:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li><strong>With Shopify:</strong> To enable app functionality through Shopify's API</li>
                    <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Hosting providers, analytics services (with data processing agreements)</li>
                    <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
                    <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger, sale, or acquisition (with notice to you)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Data Storage -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    4. Data Storage and Security
                </h2>
                
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.1 Where We Store Data</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Your data is stored on secure servers. We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your information.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.2 Security Measures</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Encrypted data transmission (HTTPS/TLS)</li>
                    <li>Secure database storage with encryption at rest</li>
                    <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
                    <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
                    <li>HMAC verification for Shopify webhooks</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Data Retention -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    5. Data Retention
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">We retain your information for as long as:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Your store has the app installed</li>
                    <li>Required for legal or regulatory purposes</li>
                    <li>Necessary to provide support or resolve disputes</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
                    When you uninstall the app, we will delete or anonymize your data within 30 days, except where retention is required by law.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Your Rights -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    6. Your Rights
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
                    <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct inaccurate information</li>
                    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your data (subject to legal requirements)</li>
                    <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
                    <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing of your data</li>
                    <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Request restriction of processing</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4">
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        <strong>To exercise these rights,</strong> please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@custompricing.task19.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">privacy@custompricing.task19.com</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- GDPR Compliance -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    7. GDPR Compliance
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">If you are in the European Economic Area (EEA), we:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>Process data lawfully, fairly, and transparently</li>
                    <li>Collect data only for specified, legitimate purposes</li>
                    <li>Keep data accurate and up to date</li>
                    <li>Store data securely and for no longer than necessary</li>
                    <li>Honor all data subject rights under GDPR</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">GDPR Data Requests</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    We handle Shopify's mandatory GDPR webhooks to respond to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-2">
                    <li>Customer data requests</li>
                    <li>Customer data erasure requests</li>
                    <li>Shop data erasure requests</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Cookies -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    8. Cookies and Tracking
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                    We use cookies and similar technologies to maintain sessions and improve user experience. Types of cookies we use:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for app functionality</li>
                    <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> To maintain your login state</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> To understand app usage (anonymized)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Third Party Services -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    9. Third-Party Services
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Our app integrates with:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li><strong>Shopify:</strong> For store data and API access</li>
                    <li><strong>Hosting Providers:</strong> For secure data storage</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">
                    These third parties have their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review them.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Children's Privacy -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    10. Children's Privacy
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Our app is not intended for individuals under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Changes to Policy -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    11. Changes to This Privacy Policy
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-2">
                    <li>Updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy</li>
                    <li>Sending a notification through the app</li>
                    <li>Emailing you at your registered email address</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">
                    Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Contact Information -->
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
                    12. Contact Us
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-green-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact Information</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@custompricing.task19.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">privacy@custompricing.task19.com</a></p>
                        <p><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@custompricing.task19.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">support@custompricing.task19.com</a></p>
                        <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://custompricing.task19.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">https://custompricing.task19.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Shopify Requirements Notice -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    Shopify App Store Compliant
                </h3>
                <p class="text-green-800 text-sm">
                    This privacy policy meets all Shopify App Store requirements for data protection, GDPR compliance, and transparency.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Footer Links -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center space-x-6">
            <a href="/terms-of-service" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">Terms of Service</a>
            <span class="text-gray-400">|</span>
            <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>
            <span class="text-gray-400">|</span>
            <a href="mailto:support@custompricing.task19.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">Contact</a>
        </div>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white border-t border-gray-200 mt-12">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6">
            <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-sm">
                © 2024 Custom Pricing & Loyalty App. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
